snippet.title: Uri terror attack: As India mourns 17 soldiers, PM, ministers discuss response

localized.description:
The bodies of the 17 soldiers killed in the terror attack at an army base in Jammu and Kashmir's Uri on Sunday are being flown back to their homes today. In Delhi, Prime Minister Narendra Modi is meeting with top ministers to shape the government's response.

Watch more videos: http://www.ndtv.com/video?yt
